{"tid":605386,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"眾說 土壤（The Soil）","createTime":"2018-03-25T15:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T15:10:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"51cc9837a1a27fdf7fdcfbd0a34a1eb5e2620785","tid":605386,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:10:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/11012/%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB-11012/%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4%EF%BC%88the-soil%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F11012%2F%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%25A3%25A4-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB-11012%2F%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%25A3%25A4%25EF%25BC%2588the-soil%25EF%25BC%2589&d=Rii%2FPha4xK9awpnXR4vtj5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=307724b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/11012/%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB-11012/%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4%EF%BC%88the-soil%EF%BC%89</a><br />\n<br />\n眾說<br />\n土壤（The Soil）<br />\n<br />\n撰文: 讀者來論 | 發佈日期: 25.03.18<br />\n<br />\n請支持《眾新聞》，成為訂戶<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n【創作者：佚名】<br />\n<br />\n作者自述：九十後攝影師／藝術家，生於香港長於香港，為這片土地感到悲傷，也同時在生活上處處感到無力，希望透過創作獲得短暫的解放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作品簡介：<br />\n<br />\n2018年3月12日，被喻為雀鳥天堂的元朗南生圍發生嚴重火災，火場面積達200平方米，大片林木被燒毀。據了解現場共發現五處火頭，起火原因有可疑。<br />\n這是南生圍八年來的第四場火，一整片蘆葦叢被無情的火燒成灰燼，腳下亦只餘下焦土。我從火場五個不同受影響的位置收集一些燒焦了的泥土樣本，然後為它們重新拍攝，再放進器皿裡進行記錄及保存。（器皿上的編號表示了採集樣本的座標，反映火場的位置分佈極廣。）<br />\n<br />\n在我眼中這些熏黑了的泥土，不只代表了大自然被破壞的證據，更正正代表了我們這一代人成長的土壤，不明不白的、了無生氣的、無力反抗的。在這樣的土壤下成長的我們，還能寄望這些土壤能種出些什麼嗎？<br />\n<br />\n註：所有泥土樣本在作品完成後均放回原處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/03/%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D-20180325140844_1b53_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%25A3%25A4-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D-20180325140844_1b53_large.jpg&h=9ce40b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樣本一 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/03/%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB-%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D-20180325140923_24e2_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%25A3%25A4-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D-20180325140923_24e2_large.jpg&h=236212c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樣本二<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/03/%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D-%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4-20180325140902_192f_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D-%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%25A3%25A4-20180325140902_192f_large.jpg&h=44b5964e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樣本三<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/03/%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB-%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D-20180325140825_e785_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%25A3%25A4-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2